  "3005660": {
    "name": "Scribe RPG",
    "steam_appid": 3005660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/ad84175995d3f082c1f2915dcd936713.webp?t=1771872080\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/ad84175995d3f082c1f2915dcd936713.poster.avif?t=1771872080\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=357 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Step into the world of ScribeRPG - an open-world action-adventure RPG. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Immerse yourself in rich, branching dialogues laced with sharp, sarcastic humor, epic quests, dynamic real time combat, crafting, stealth, archery, magic, and so much more. ScribeRPG is a game where its own lore is the most important part of the gameplay. All brought to life with beautifully handcrafted pixel art.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/f6df389ab9a1766b70cc01e887698898.poster.avif?t=1771872080\" width=800 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/f6df389ab9a1766b70cc01e887698898.webm?t=1771872080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You will experience a feature rich RPG that seamlessly blends the magic of classic point and click adventures, the thrill of action games, and the cleverness of late ’80s puzzle platformers, all without the limits of old technology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> ScribeRPG pushes pixel art to its limits and harnesses modern tools to deliver gameplay and content that were never possible in the early days of computer games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/51830d68b5cd02f16f4152fefbd62d3d.webp?t=1771872080\" width=800 height=7 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><i>In ScribeRPG, </i>you step into the boots of a rogue, yet somewhat naive, Scribe<i> on a daring quest to uncover and record the true history of the Continent.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Imprisoned on a remote island monastery, you witness history being erased, records destroyed, books rewritten, art defaced, all to serve the new Emperor’s dogma. Which, as you’d expect, is simply: <i>‘I am GOD, and nothing else matters.’</i> From that day on, being a scholar became much easier. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/ff8b5574b99c4812f847eec5c4ad24d7.poster.avif?t=1771872080\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/ff8b5574b99c4812f847eec5c4ad24d7.webm?t=1771872080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/ff8b5574b99c4812f847eec5c4ad24d7.mp4?t=1771872080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Not for You! You refuse to let history be erased. Escaping the island, you embark on a perilous quest across the <strong>Continent</strong> to reclaim its lost truths. But don’t expect to study it in a dusty library - not anymore. Those halls now serve as dance floors for the Emperor’s mistresses. To uncover the truth, you must chase it to its roots: <strong>hidden tombs, dark dungeons, deep forests, and towering peaks.</strong> Only there can the lost pieces of the past be reclaimed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">But it’s a crime against the <strong>Emperor</strong>, and the mission must remain hidden as the eyes and ears of his spies watch your every move… <strong>beware, you will be hunted!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/5b2069e4d0ee752f75791576f48fbe6f.poster.avif?t=1771872080\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/5b2069e4d0ee752f75791576f48fbe6f.webm?t=1771872080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005660/extras/5b2069e4d0ee752f75791576f48fbe6f.mp4?t=1771872080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
